s..... other than being able to pull and do the FD rez trick I suppose... but that doesnt make up the difference........... yes, I would like to see us become more balanced...</P><P>As a final note... I do have to say that mindwrack, as it gives 300 mana to each party member once per minute (basicaly), does a lot to give us grouping credibility........ the ability to give an entire party flowing thought 30! is amazing..... its just a matter of training the myopicly snobish members of other classes about how effective it is.</P><P><BR>Ashnar Blackbone<BR>Warlock, Duckmaster<BR>Innoruuk</P><P> </font></td>
